cs.CR, cs.IOT, cs.DC, cs.DB, cs.LG 

The paper discusses privacy-preserving fog computing for SVD computation in the context of IoT, which involves security and privacy concerns (cs.CR), IoT (cs.IOT), and data analysis (cs.DB) in a distributed computing environment (cs.DC). Additionally, the paper proposes a flexible framework that can be applied to different applications, which involves machine learning (cs.LG).
